  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "年は2142年。あなたは記憶を失った男、コンラッド・B・ハートを操作します。敵対的なエイリアンからなんとか逃げた後、コンラッドのバイクは未知の惑星でクラッシュします。コンラッドはジャングルに迷い込み、ここから彼の生存と失ったアイデンティティを求める冒険が始まります。\n\n「フラッシュバック」はプラットフォームアクションアドベンチャーです。コンラッドをプラットフォーム上で移動させ、さまざまなアクションを行います。単純にジャンプしたり、長いランニングジャンプをしたり、走ったり、登ったり、 ledge にぶら下がったり、地面に落ちている物を拾ったりすることができます。自分を守るために、銃で敵を撃ったり、石などのさまざまな物を使って敵を攻撃したり、気をそらしたりします。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Throughout the 20th century, an unprecedented political and economic crisis afflicted Earth, leading to the systematic disabling of it's programme to conquer outer space through lack of funding. The highest priority now was to carryout research into new energy sources, preservation of the enviro- ment and maintenance of the cultural heritage. However, at the dawn of the 21st century, provision of considerable funds from an unknown source released by the politicians of the new, unified government, permitted a return to the space research programme.\n\nThe conquest began gradually with the construction of huge, manned artificial satellites. Several lunar bases were created with the view to becoming future Earth colonies within the solar system. The considerable advancements made together with the supply of increasingly greater sums of money allowed man to explore, even as far as the planet Titan.\n\nYou play the part of Conrad Hart, controlling his every move through the 6 levels of the game. During your quest, you will come across many different friends and foes whom you may wish to help or vanquish using your gun. you will have to complete many challenges in order to restore your lost memory. Each level features its own unique graphics and hazards, linked by cinematic animation sequences.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
